This will help you for windows system operations

1. How to check applications running on which ports and other useful things
-> open "Resource monitor" using windows serach -> then check "Network tab"

2. How to start stop any windows service like grafana
-> Open "Services" using windows search -> check respective service and right click on it -> start/stop

3. To search every file in the current directory and all subdirectories that contained the word Windows, regardless of the letter case, type:
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/findstr
findstr /s /i Windows *.*